## Data Flow After Changes

```mermaid
graph TD
    A[PDF Upload] --> B[doc-agent: pdfplumber OCR]
    B --> C{Text > 100 chars?}
    C -->|Yes| D[Groq LLM: Extract Financial JSON]
    C -->|No| E[Tesseract OCR Fallback]
    E --> D
    D --> F[PATCH financials namespace]
    D --> G[Compute DSCR/ICR/Leverage]
    G --> H[PATCH derived_features namespace]
    F --> I[gst-agent reads real revenue]
    F --> J[bank-recon-agent reads real turnover]
    H --> K[model-selector reads real features]
    K --> L[risk-agent: UNIQUE score per PDF]
    L --> M[stress-agent: REAL DSCR stress test]
    M --> N[CAM: ALL real numbers, zero placeholders]
```

